OL,3,CInsulating Your Home: How To Beat The
OL,4,CScammers
OL,6,FEnergy bills are on the rise again,
OL,7,Fwith the energy price cap from January
OL,8,F1 to March 31 2026 being set at #1,758
OL,9,Fper year for a typical household.
OL,11,FSo people are looking for ways to save
OL,12,Fmoney on their energy bills, and for
OL,13,Fsome, grants offering energy-efficient
OL,14,Fhome improvements, seemed like a
OL,15,Flifeline. But as ITV's Tonight
OL,16,Fprogramme reveals, for many it's
OL,17,Fturned into a nightmare. The programme
OL,18,Ffound homeowners left with damp, leaks
OL,19,Fand mould in their properties
OL,20,Ffollowing work being carried out.
