OL,4,CScammers
OL,6,FCharlotte Hawkins has been
OL,7,Finvestigating how people can have
OL,8,Fconfidence in who to trust when it
OL,9,Fcomes to getting green home
OL,10,Fimprovements.
OL,12,FThere have been a number of different
OL,13,Fgovernment-backed schemes that
OL,14,Fhouseholders, if they are receiving
OL,15,Fcertain benefits or have a
OL,16,Fparticularly inefficient home, can
OL,17,Fapply to have green home improvement
OL,18,Fsuch as heat pumps, insulation and
OL,19,Fsolar panels installed. These schemes
OL,20,Fare funded through householders'
OL,21,Fenergy bills.
