OL,4,CScammers
OL,6,FTonight spoke to someone who qualified
OL,7,F- Steve, a retired builder who was
OL,8,Fspurred into thinking about upgrading
OL,9,Fhis house after suffering health
OL,10,Fproblems. In 2024, interior
OL,11,Finsulation, a heat pump, a new water
OL,12,Ftank and solar panels were fitted to
OL,13,Fhis home. But he was left with heating
OL,14,Fproblems, and discovered that the new
OL,15,Fwater tank was leaking. The company
OL,16,Fwho carried out the work has since
OL,17,Fapologised, and offered to rectify any
OL,18,Foutstanding defects.
