OL,6,FIn Telford, a company named Skilled
OL,7,FMapping is using thermal images to
OL,8,Fassess how effective insulation
OL,9,Fschemes have been. CEO Alex
OL,10,FWrigglesworth has scanned over half a
OL,11,Fmillion homes across the UK that have
OL,12,Fhad different types of insulation
OL,13,Fretrofitted. He told Tonight:
OL,15,F"Pretty much every house that is
OL,16,Fretrofitted with cavity wall
OL,17,Finsulation that we've thermal imaged
OL,18,Fwe see near total failure rates."
