OL,6,FIn October, the National Audit Office
OL,7,Festimated 98 percent of all external
OL,8,Fwall insulation fitted under one of
OL,9,Fthe government-backed initiatives,
OL,10,FECO4, has been found to be faulty -
OL,11,Faffecting tens of thousands of homes.
OL,12,FIn last week's budget, the government
OL,13,Fannounced they were scrapping the
OL,14,Fscheme.
