OL,6,FTonight also looked into 'energy-
OL,7,Fsaving plugs' that claim to save
OL,8,Fpeople huge amounts of money on their
OL,9,Felectricity bills. Consumer insight
OL,10,Fcompany Which? tested the plugs,
OL,11,Ffinding no evidence that they could
OL,12,Fcut bills, and that they also failed
OL,13,Fto meet basic electrical safety
OL,14,Fstandards.
